ramming, keyboards {{small|(track 10)}}\n* [[MNEK]] \u2013 background vocals, (drums & keys)programming {{small|(track 12)}}, additional vocals {{small|(track 18)}}\n* Kali Claire McLoughlin \u2013 background vocals {{small|(track 17)}}\n* Nick Trygstad \u2013 cello {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* Simon Turner \u2013 cello {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* Paulette Bayley \u2013 violin {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* Peter Whitfield \u2013 violin {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* Sarah Brandwood-Spencer \u2013 violin {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* [[Tre Jean-Marie]] \u2013 bass, piano, strings, synthesizer {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* [[Josh Werner]] \u2013 bass guitar {{small|(track 2)}}\n* Chris Laws \u2013 drums {{small|(tracks 3, 8)}}\n* [[Steve Mac]] \u2013 keyboards {{small|(tracks 3, 8)}}\n* Tim Laws \u2013 guitar {{small|(tracks 3, 8)}}\n* [[Al Shux]] \u2013 bass, drums, [[Key (instrument)|key]]s {{small|(track 5)}}\n* [[Fraser T. Smith]] \u2013 drum programming {{small|(tracks 6, 10)}}, keyboards {{small|(track 10)}}\n* [[Jordan Riley]] \u2013 drums, keyboards {{small|(tracks 7, 13)}}, synthesizer programming {{small|(track 7)}}, bass, piano {{small|(track 13)}}\n* Lewis Allen \u2013 guitar {{small|(track 9)}} \n* Leo Kalyan \u2013 (drums & keys)programming {{small|(track 12)}}\n* [[Stephen Kozmeniuk]] \u2013 drums, strings {{small|(track 12)}}\n* [[Jimmy Napes]] \u2013 piano {{small|(track 13)}}\n* [[Marlon Roudette]] \u2013 electric guitar {{small|(track 16)}}\n* Alastair \"AoD\" O'Donnell \u2013 guitar {{small|(track 17)}}\n* [[Jax Jones|Timucin Lam]] \u2013 all instruments {{small|(track 18)}}\n* Twice as Nice \u2013 drum, synthesizer programming {{small|(track 19)}}\n* Charlie Handsome \u2013 synthesizer programming, drums {{small|(track 19)}}\n* Josh Crocker \u2013 drums, keyboards {{small|(track 20)}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Production===\n{{div col}}\n* Tre Jean-Marie \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* [[Dre Skull]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 2)}}\n* [[Wildlife!|WILDLIFE!]] \u2013 additional production {{small|(track 2)}}\n* Cameron Gower Poole \u2013 (additional) vocal production {{small|(tracks 2, 11-12)}} \n* Steve Mac \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 3, 8, 21(bonus))}} \n* Oak \u2013 production {{small|(track 4)}}\n* Al Shux \u2013 production {{small|(track 5)}}\n* Fraser T. Smith \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 6, 10)}}\n* Jordan Riley \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 7, 13)}}\n* MakeYouKnowLove \u2013 production {{small|(track 9)}}\n* Tyrell Paul \u2013 production {{small|(track 10)}}\n* [[Snakehips (duo)|Snakehips]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* [[MXXWLL]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* MNEK \u2013 production {{small|(track 12)}}\n* KOZ \u2013 production {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Leo Kalyan \u2013 additional production {{small|(track 12)}}\n* JD. Reid \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 15-16, 20, 22(bonus))}}\n* Alastair \"AoD\" O'Donnell \u2013 additional production {{small|(track 17)}}\n* Jay Weathers \u2013 production {{small|(track 17)}}\n* Jax Jones - production {{small|(track 18)}}\n* [[Mark Ralph (record producer)|Mark Ralph]] - co-production {{small|(track 18)}}\n* Twice as Nice \u2013 production {{small|(track 19)}}\n* Charlie Handsome \u2013 production {{small|(track 19)}}\n* Josh Crocker \u2013 production {{small|(track 20)}}\n* GA \u2013 production {{small|(track 22(bonus))}}\n* [[Joel Pott]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 23(bonus))}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Technical===\n{{div col}}\n* Tre Jean-Marie \u2013 programming {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* Nosa Apollo \u2013 programming {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* Geoff Swan \u2013 mixing {{small|(tracks 1, 7, 14-15)}}\n* Lewis Chapman \u2013 assistant mixing {{small|(tracks 1, 14)}}\n* Bill Zimmerman \u2013 additional engineering {{small|(tracks 2, 5)}}\n* [[Phil Tan]] \u2013 mixing {{small|(tracks 2, 5)}}\n* [[Dann Pursey|Dan Pursey]] \u2013 engineering {{small|(tracks 3, 8)}}\n* Chris Laws \u2013 engineering {{small|(tracks 3, 8)}}\n* [[Spike Stent|Mark \"Spike\" Stent]] \u2013 mixing {{small|(tracks 3-4, 8-9, 12)}}\n* Al Shux \u2013 recording {{small|(track 5)}}\n* [[Manny Marroquin]] \u2013 mixing {{small|(track 6)}}\n* Chris Galland - engineering {{small|(track 6)}}\n* Jordan Riley \u2013 recording {{small|(track 7)}}\n* Niko Battistini \u2013 mix assistant {{small|(track 7)}}\n* Michael Freeman \u2013 mix assistant {{small|(track 9)}}\n* Wez Clarke \u2013 additional programming {{small|(tracks 10, 13, 20)}}, mixing {{small|(tracks 10, 13, 16, 20)}}\n* Cameron Gower Poole \u2013 mixing {{small|(track 11)}}, recording {{small|(track 12)}}\n* MNEK \u2013 background vocals recording {{small|(track 12)}}\n* [[Five Finger Death Punch#Members|Matt Snell]] \u2013 assistant engineering {{small|(track 12)}}\n* JD. Reid \u2013 engineering {{small|(track 15)}}, programming {{small|(tracks 15-16)}}\n* Jay Weathers \u2013 engineering {{small|(track 17)}}\n* [[Mike Spencer]] \u2013 additional engineering, mixing {{small|(track 17)}}\n* Mark Ralph \u2013 mixing {{small|(track 18)}}\n* Jamie Snell \u2013 editing {{small|(track 18)}}\n* [[Dan Parry]] \u2013 mixing {{small|(track 19)}}\n* Josh Crocker \u2013 programming {{small|(track 20)}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Artwork=== \n{{div col}}\n* [[Mariano Vivanco]] \u2013 photography\n* Ted Lovett (Studio) \u2013 art direction and design\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australian Albums ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2019/08/aria-chart-watch-537/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #537|publisher=auspOp|date=10 August 2019|accessdate=10 August 2019}}</ref>\n| 70\n|-\n{{album chart|Flanders|50|artist=Mabel %5BUK%5D|album=High Expectations|rowheader=true|accessdate=9 August 2019|refname=Flanders}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Wallonia|