Jinde Meriye {{!}} New Punjabi Movie {{!}} First Look {{!}} Dainik Savera |url=https://www.dainiksaveratimes.com/saveratvvideo/361a92987836cc |work=www.dainiksaveratimes.com |language=hi}}</ref>, Yuvraj Hans and Navneet Kaur Dhillon in the lead roles<ref>{{cite web |title=Jinde Meriye First Look: Sonam Bajwa reunites with Parmish Verma for Pankaj Batra\u2019s romantic movie |url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/news/jinde-meriye-first-look-sonam-bajwa-reunites-parmish-verma-pankaj-batra-s-romantic-movie-488661 |website=PINKVILLA |language=en}}</ref> The film is produced by [[Pankaj Batra]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Sonam Bajwa, Parmish Verma in Jinde Meriye; first look poster out |url=https://www.thestatesman.com/entertainment/sonam-bajwa-parmish-verma-jinde-meriye-first-look-poster-1502827102.html |website=The Statesman |date=27 November 2019}}</ref>, Ashu Munish Sahni<ref>{{cite web |title=Jinde Meriye Movie Trailer {{!}} Review {{!}} Story {{!}} Cast {{!}} Songs {{!}} Release Date |url=https://punjabipollywood.com/jinde-meriye-movie/ |website=PunjabiPollywood.com |language=en |date=25 February 2019}}</ref>, Aniket Kawade, Preeta Batra and Amandeep Singh<ref>{{cite news |title=Parmish Verma and Sonam Bajwa\u2019s Second Movie \u2018Jinde Meriye\u2019 first poster Released |url=https://getindianews.com/entertainment/pollywood/parmish-verma-and-sonam-bajwas-second-movie-jinde-meriye-first-poster-released/19674/ |work=Get India News |date=27 November 2019}}</ref> and co-produced by Mandip Dhami. It was released in cinemas on 24 January 2020. <ref>{{cite web |title=Jinde Meriye Movie |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/punjabi/movie-details/jinde-meriye/movieshow/68148779.cms}}</ref>\n\n==Synopsis== \nYaadi, a happy-go-lucky person, and Rehmat are childhood friends who turned love birds and planned to get married. Rehmat`s family is against the decision as Yaadi carries a careless attitude towards his future. To get Rehmat, Yaadi must stand on his own and have a prosperous career. However, Yaadi chooses an illegal way to be successful, which infuriates Rehmat, making her leave Yaadi forever. Will Yaadi be able to win Rehmat back? A trailer movie Jinde Meriye has been released. The trailer of this movie shows the extent to which human beings strive to fulfill their dreams in life \u2013 with two hearts of love.<ref>{{cite web |title=Jinde Meriye Movie (2020) {{!}} Reviews, Cast & Release Date in |url=https://www.trendpunjabi.com/jinde-meriye-parmish-verma-full-punjabi-movie-cast/ |website=Trend Punjabi |language=en}}</ref> This movie fully packed with Drama, Comedy, and Romance. Even we will get to see our favorite Punjabi music artist Goldy Khalon as well. He has contributed Numerours of hit Punjabi songs to the Punjabi music industry <ref>{{cite web |title=Jinde Meriye Movie (2020) {{!}} Cast & Release Date |url=https://in.bookmyshow.com/movies/jinde-meriye/ET00097403/ |website=BookMyShow |language=en}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Parmish Verma]]\n* [[Sonam Bajwa]]\n* [[Yuvraj Hans]]\n* [[Navneet Kaur Dhillon]]\n* [[Hobby Dhaliwal]]\n* [[Anita Devgan]]\n* [[Hardeep Gill]]\n* [[Malkeet Rauni]]\n* [[Ravinder Mand]]\n== Soundtrack ==\n{{Infobox album\n| name       = Jinde Meriye\n| type       = Soundtrack\n| artist     = Desi Crew, Troy Arif, DJ Strings\n| cover      = \n| alt        =\n| released   = 23 January 2020\n| recorded   = 2019\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Film soundtrack|Feature film soundtrack]]\n| language   = [[Punjabi language|Punjabi]]\n| length     = 16:30\n| label      = Times Music\n| producer   =\n| prev_title = \n| prev_year  = \n| next_title = \n| next_year  = \n| misc = {{External media\n| audio1 = {{YouTube|WHP0nIEQY0Y|Audio Jukebox}}}}\n}}\n\nSoundtrack of the film was composed by Desi Crew, Troy Arif and DJ Strings whereas lyrics were penned by Mandeep Mavi, Laddi Chahal, Sukh Sohal and Kahlon. \n  \n{{Track listing\n| headline     = Track listing\n| extra_column = Si